      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an impeccable E46 M3, a benchmark of atmospheric engineering. Power is delivered by the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double-VANOS system, producing a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. This example features a factory Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock for precise torque distribution. The chassis remains structurally flawless with documented subframe reinforcement and original suspension kinematics. This specimen retains factory-spec compression and leak-down figures, ensuring mechanical integrity matches its concourse-level aesthetics.",
